{"tid":1077843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始殺完隻泰國狗奇,香港就即爆麻疹 ! 因果報應","createTime":"2019-03-26T00:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T02:25:10.000Z","uid":65346,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb5f4db657c277b08c544549ae6ed91ecf1174b","tid":1077843,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1449537-20190325.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1449537-20190325.htm&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=9f27244b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1449537-20190325.htm&h=b87ccc13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1449537-20190325.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n仲死口話無 !"},{"pid":"b17c8028e9b4ad13cc681004c0ba27c146ef840e","tid":1077843,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:45:51.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，香港社區對麻疹的防疫力相當高，社區層面並無爆發的跡象。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始說，2015至2018年本港的麻疹個案每年維持20宗以內，不過，香港旅客出入境頻繁，而且有外國爆發麻疹，因此近日錄得的確診個案都屬外地傳入，主要涉及本港機場員工。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，下午聽取衞生署匯報最新情況，本港今年至今錄得20宗確診個案，因應機場的麻疹爆發，上周五已在機場設立疫苗接種站，今日亦增加了接種站數目及接種時段。如果在機場有更多人接種，署方會與機場診所商討疫苗接種細節。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又說，當局已與麻疹疫苗供應商聯絡，亦有發信予醫學會及有關醫學團體，並向私家醫生提供疫苗供應聯絡資訊。<br />\n<br />\n機場唔 L 係社區 ?!<br />\n機場 d 人唔會出市區! DKLM !<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ef27a0b9fca61ed5d86c3aeffadc54fed7b66c","tid":1077843,"uid":124410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n有預感好快大爆發"},{"pid":"cc0f75772938c065a621cc3ea16b97312c0a87e7","tid":1077843,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34ef27a0b9fca61ed5d86c3aeffadc54fed7b66c","tid":1077843,"uid":124410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:56:24.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n有預感好快大爆發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:59:31.000Z","msg":"已爆,樓價大下跌...<br />\n疫苗, Salt, 醋會炒到幾千萬得少少 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6a31c26298976c2f8df70985f5172c01455659","tid":1077843,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32da424cfca723e85fe5eebfacc472c1899b211","tid":1077843,"uid":214972,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔殺爆瘋狗症就真係報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492380ad3b69cab4e8cdcca77bbe135d27c036d0","tid":1077843,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d32da424cfca723e85fe5eebfacc472c1899b211","tid":1077843,"uid":214972,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔殺爆瘋狗症就真係報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"隻狗無瘋狗症都爆到瘋狗症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1735de33cc8c89b07db3c29c9e421fd12ecde537","tid":1077843,"uid":56819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"492380ad3b69cab4e8cdcca77bbe135d27c036d0","tid":1077843,"uid":37389,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d32da424cfca723e85fe5eebfacc472c1899b211","tid":1077843,"uid":214972,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"唔殺爆瘋狗症就真係報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T02:02:51.000Z","msg":"隻狗無瘋狗症都爆到瘋狗症？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\